      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is a commercially validated CFD solver with documented V&V test suite. Solver release notes confirm regression testing against 350+ benchmark cases. Internal SQA audit log (ref: UofA-SQA-2024-03) documents version control, build verification, and access control procedures consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Achieved Gradation 2 exceeds the Gradation 1 required at MRL 2 for this COU."
