      "rationale": "Code verification for the Navier-Stokes solver kernel was confirmed via the Method of Manufactured Solutions (MMS) applied to a rotating-frame incompressible flow problem representative of the CBP impeller domain. Observed order of accuracy (1.97 ± 0.04) is consistent with the solver's nominal second-order spatial discretization. ANSYS published benchmark suite (ANSYS-FV-BM-2023) further corroborates solver correctness for rotating machinery flows. Achieved Gradation 2 satisfies and exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
